><h3>Basis for recommendation</h3><!-- end field 2024eb69-3ecf-494a-81e1-e12f963fe002 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 2a9345fd-730a-4963-a983-81e20a717219 --><!-- begin field c828adde-ad2f-472d-9f78-db917fe52e7d --><p>This information is based on expert opinion in a guideline on the<em> </em>diagnosis and management of acute and chronic urticaria [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/urticaria/references/\">Bernstein, 2014</a>] and in review articles on urticaria [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/urticaria/references/\">Wanderer et al, 2000</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/urticaria/references/\">Pierson, 2006</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/urticaria/references/\">Jafilan, 2015</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/urticaria/references/\">Marzano, 2015</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/urticaria/references/\">BMJ, 2016</a>].</p><!-- end field c828adde-ad2f-472d-9f78-db917fe52e7d --><!-- end item 2a9345fd-730a-4963-a983-81e20a717219 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}